## Quick Reference Checklist

### Before Creating a Dashboard:
- [ ] Use template variables for filtering?
- [ ] Limited to 10-15 panels?
- [ ] Appropriate default time range (6h)?
- [ ] Consistent units across panels?
- [ ] Panel descriptions added?

### Before Writing LogQL Queries:
- [ ] Using specific label selectors (not wildcards)?
- [ ] Line filters applied early?
- [ ] Appropriate time range selected?
- [ ] JSON parsing after line filters?

### Before Writing PromQL Queries:
- [ ] Using rate() for counters?
- [ ] Appropriate time window (5m)?
- [ ] Aggregating by necessary labels only?
- [ ] Consider using recording rules?

